text: Barbara Gross (born 20 November 1993) is a German wheelchair basketball player. She won a silver medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played at the 2015 Women's U25 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship and 2018 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship. She played for University of Alabama. == References == Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic silver medalists for Germany Category:German wheelchair basketball players
